content.text: Open up the browser and go to https://www.google.com

I'll help you open Firefox and navigate to Google. Let me break this down into steps:

1. First, I'll take a screenshot to see the desktop
2. Locate Firefox icon
3. Right-click on Firefox
4. Click "Open"
5. Once Firefox is open, I'll navigate to Google
